Class AdjListNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.gla.dcs.tp3.w.algorithm.AdjListNode

  • public class AdjListNode
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a node of the network graph. The class has three instance variables representing the flow and capacity of the edge, and which vertex the edge points to.
